answers.answer: This urinalysis has nothing to do with diabetes. Diabetes is tested by blood test. As for whether you have a UTI, I would recommend asking the doctor who had the test ordered. He should have scheduled you for a follow up or at least a phonecall to explain the results and prescribe treatment.
